rgy, willingness, and happiness as possible.', 2057, 0), (88138, 'Barnby always dismissed the idea of intelligence in a woman as no more than a characteristic to be endured.', 11267, 0), (88139, 'Daydreams of wealth or women must have given Carolo that faraway look which never left him; sad and silent, he contemplated huge bank balances and voluptuous revels.', 11267, 0), (88140, 'There is something magical and transformational about saying “yes” to God. When you take His hand, step out of that boat (your ordinary, comfortable life), and be brave. Instead of spending your lifetime living in fear and playing it safe, you boldly walk in obedience. God makes you brave.', 7289, 0), (88141, 'Only beards can''t make you count as a man, you need to have respect for women in your heart for that.', 12388, 0), (88142, 'Old or young, light or dark, full or frail, every woman has qualities that make her beautiful.', 17002, 0), (88143, 'I rather miss my wild girl; but if I get a strong, helpful, tender-hearted woman in her place, I shall feel quite satisfied.', 296, 0), (88144, 'It makes you love vividly, work intensely, and realize that, in the scheme of things, you really don''t have time to sit on the sofa in your undies watching Homes Under the Hammer.', 2057, 0), (88145, 'The aphorism "If you want something done, ask a busy woman" is in direct acknowledgment of the efficiency boot camp parenthood puts you through.', 2057, 0), (88146, 'Strong women are the universe’s way of enhancing the strength of men.', 17002, 0), (88147, 'And it''s time people told the truth about beautiful women. They do not shimmer down staircases. They do not descend, as was once supposed, from on high, attached to nothing other than wings.', 825, 0), (88148, 'We ask no sympathy from others in the anxiety and agony of a  INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (88151, 'How the little courtesies of life on the surface of society, deemed so important from man towards woman, fade into u